# SPRING_BOOT_RESTAPI_BASE64_HMACSHA256
LATIHAN PEMBUATAN REST API DENGAN MENGGUNAKAN ANNOTASI HEADER, PEMBUATAN TOKEN HMACSHA256 untuk security dan upload images menggunakan Base64 Encoding dan Decoding

# API SPECS
Berikut ini ada spesifikasi API Yang Di gunakan pada project ini

## GET ALL BIODATA
    Method : GET 
    Endpoint : http://localhost:8080/api/v1/biodata/getAllBiodata 
    Header : 
    Content-Type : application/json 
    Response : 
    {
    "data": [
        {
            "id": 2,
            "nim": "4321",
            "fullName": "Mohammad Sulaeman",
            "photo": "4321_Mohammad Sulaeman.jpeg",
            "email": "mohammadsulaeman22@gmail.com",
            "phone": "628380821311212",
            "dob": "Jakarta 23 Juni 1990",
            "address": "Bekasi"
        }
    ],
    "message": "datalist ditemukan",
    "statusCode": "ACCEPTED",
    "status": "success"
    }

## GET IMAGES
    Method : GET
    Endpoint : http://localhost:8080/api/v1/biodata/images/{imagesName}
    Header : 
    Content-Type : image/jpeg
## SAVE BIODATA
    Method : POST 
    Endpoint : http://localhost:8080/api/v1/biodata/save 
    Header :
    Content-Type: application/json 
    Token: HMACSHA256 
    Body : 
    {
    "address": "Bekasi",
    "dob": "Jakarta 23 Juni 1990",
    "email": "mohammadsulaeman22@gmail.com",
    "fullName": "Mohammad Sulaeman",
    "nim": "4321",
    "phone": "628380821311212",
    "photo": ""
    }
    Response : 
    {
      "data": {
          "id": 2,
          "nim": "4321",
          "fullName": "Mohammad Sulaeman",
          "photo": "4321_Mohammad Sulaeman.jpeg",
          "email": "mohammadsulaeman22@gmail.com",
          "phone": "628380821311212",
          "dob": "Jakarta 23 Juni 1990",
          "address": "Bekasi"
      },
      "message": "Data Berhasil Tersimpan",
      "statusCode": "201 CREATED",
      "status": "success"
    }

## UPDATE BIODATA
    Method : PUT
    Endpoint : http://localhost:8080/api/v1/biodata/update/{nim}
    Header : 
    Content-Type: application/json 
    Token: HMACSHA256 
    Body : 
    {
      "address": "Bekasi",
      "dob": "Jakarta 23 Juni 1990",
      "email": "mohammadsulaeman22@gmail.com",
      "fullName": "Mohammad Sulaeman",
      "nim": "4321",
      "phone": "628380821311212",
      "photo": ""
    }
    Response : 
    {
    "data": "BiodataDto(id=2, nim=4321, fullName=Mohammad Sulaeman, photo=4321_Mohammad Sulaeman.jpeg, email=mohammadsulaeman22@gmail.com, phone=628380821311212, dob=Jakarta 23 Juni 1990, address=Bekasi)",
    "message": "Data Berhasil Di Update",
    "statusCode": "201 CREATED",
    "status": "success"
    }

  ## DELETE BIODATA

      {
